name: complex_arith_add_of_differences_regroups
section: arithmetic-normalization
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: The sum of two differences should regroup to subtract the sum of subtrahends.
law: (= (fuzz-add (fuzz-sub {a} {b}) (fuzz-sub {c} {d})) (fuzz-sub (fuzz-add {a} {c}) (fuzz-add {b} {d})))
